Recipe Finder is a full-stack web application that allows users to discover, add, update, and manage recipes. Built using React, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB Atlas, this app provides a seamless experience for food enthusiasts to organize and explore recipes.

Features

✅ Recipe List – View all available recipes with clickable links to detailed pages.
✅ Add Recipe – Users can add new recipes with ingredients and cooking instructions.
✅ Recipe Details – Displays full recipe information on a dedicated page.
✅ Update & Delete – Users can edit or remove recipes easily.
